{"id":"808266651712815104","type":"text","timestamp":1770823146,"post_url":"https://www.tumblr.com/blog/view/goodtransgirl/808266651712815104","is_reblog":true,"added_content":false,"tags":[],"reblog_ready":false,"body":"<p><a class=\"tumblr_blog\" href=\"https://coldbrewpup.tumblr.com/post/784735416710529024\">coldbrewpup</a>:</p><blockquote><p><a class=\"tumblr_blog\" href=\"https://www.tumblr.com/blog/view/emmacandle/784735078741934081\">emmacandle</a>:</p><blockquote><p><a class=\"tumblr_blog\" href=\"https://coldbrewpup.tumblr.com/post/784734962713853952/listen-if-i-didnt-respond-with-a-blushing-as\">coldbrewpup</a>:</p><blockquote><p><a class=\"tumblr_blog\" href=\"https://www.tumblr.com/blog/view/emmacandle/784734781362552833\">emmacandle</a>:</p><blockquote><h1>HOW ARE YOU SUPPOSED TO PUNISH A KNIGHT WHO BLUSHES AND SMILES EVERY TIME YOU TRY</h1></blockquote><p>listen, if i <i>didn&rsquo;t </i>respond with a blushing &ldquo;as you wish, my lady&rdquo; and squirm a little about it then what kind of loyal knight would i even be?</p></blockquote><h1>YOU COULD AT LEAST <i>PRETEND</i> THAT YOU DONT LIKE IT</h1></blockquote><div class=\"npf_row\"><figure class=\"tmblr-full\" data-orig-height=\"271\" data-orig-width=\"540\"><img src=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/c63eecae011c5623ee01ca077568cc58/c61eb6db62ab6c97-ca/s640x960/6143692c46fc8b7eb26f5ba65a5a12b78067ae8b.jpg\" data-orig-height=\"271\" data-orig-width=\"540\" srcset=\"h","trail":[{"blog":{"name":"emmacandle"},"post":{"id":"784734781362552833"}},{"blog":{"name":"coldbrewpup"},"post":{"id":"784734962713853952"}},{"blog":{"name":"emmacandle"},"post":{"id":"784735078741934081"}},{"blog":{"name":"coldbrewpup"},"post":{"id":"784735416710529024"}}],"baseline_notes":21140,"baseline_ts":1774705101.464}